column14: Significant comorbidities (e.g., cancer, cardiovascular disease, diabetes)
column26: Symptoms at disease onset (e.g.,  mild fever, cough (dry), sore throat, nasal congestion, malaise, headache, muscle pain, or malaise)
column33: Admission from institution (prison, nursing home, etc)
column34: Current symptoms (e.g.,  mild fever, cough (dry), sore throat, nasal congestion, malaise, headache, muscle pain, or malaise)
column57: Potential candidate for donation of convalescent plasma (Y/N)
column63: Other cytokines (e.g., IFN-gamma, TNF-alpha, IL-1, GM-CSF)
column89: SARS-CoV-2 RNA Detection-Qualitative (e.g. detected or not detected)
column90: SARS-CoV-2 RNA Level-Quantitative (e.g., Ct value, or copies/mL)
column92: Virus amino acid substitution data, including viral target protein, specific amino acid position and substitution, and frequency in population (this is very high level and no doubt we would have a request for more detailed resistance data)
column93: SARS-CoV-2 IgM, IgG or Neutralizing Antibody (e.g., ELISA titer or PRNT50 titer)
column94: Serum cytokine (e.g., IFN-gamma, TNF-alpha, IL-1, GM-CSF)
